## Additional Terms

### Academic Use
This software is designed for educational and academic purposes. When used in 
academic institutions, proper attribution to the original author is appreciated.

### Commercial Use
Commercial use is permitted under the MIT License terms. For large-scale 
commercial deployments, consider contributing back to the project or supporting
the development.

### Blockchain Technology Disclaimer
This project implements a simplified blockchain for educational and demonstration
purposes. For production use in critical certificate verification systems, 
additional security measures and blockchain implementations should be considered.

### No Warranty
This software is provided without warranty. Users are responsible for ensuring
the security and reliability of their certificate verification systems.

